[12:10] <patrickb> In WrappableBuffer there is this optional optimization with `span-line-start($start)`. Can I get a quick explanation how to use that? I guess I somehow need to feed my domain knowledge into that function (in my case each line group I inserted encompasses exactly one logical line).

[12:26] <patrickb> Also, is using `post-process-line-group()` the right approach to add additional highlighting to lines? I'd like to highlight the line where the program is currently stopped.

